milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (419) involving teams Australia & Pakistan in ODIs
Javed Miandad and Mudassar Nazar's 105-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 88 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Zaheer Abbas
